496
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:44,640
Go on.

497
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:45,960
Coming right up!

498
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:48,240
Would you like anything to drink?

499
00:21:49,240 --> 00:21:49,760
Just

