00:21:55,280 --> 00:21:56,160
What are we drinking?

504
00:21:58,760 --> 00:21:59,760
Who said there's no wine?

505
00:22:02,920 --> 00:22:04,960
Isn't this the grape wine
that Xuanxuan brewed?

506
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:09,040
It's been a while
since I've had my wife's grape wine.

507
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:10,440
Here.

508
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:11,080
Your cups.

509
00:22:11,140 --> 00:22:12,460
Didn't expect this, did you?

510
00:22:12,520 --> 00:22:13,320
I even made

511
00:22:13,320 --> 00:22:15,320
a trip back to get it.

512
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:22,200
Here.

513
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:25,240
- Cheers!
- Here!

514
00:22:36,120 --> 00:22:36,680
Xuanxuan?

515
00:22:38,040 --> 00:22:39,140
What's gotten into you?

516
00:22:42,360 --> 00:22:43,280
Xuanxuan found out

517
00:22:43,400 --> 00:22:44,040
that Sun Yi

518
00:22:44,040 --> 00:22:44,760
and Master Zhang

519
00:22:44,760 --> 00:22:45,880
are nowhere to be found.

520
00:22:46,040 --> 00:22:47,120
And the painter is dead.

521
00:22:47,480 --> 00:22:48,160
What?

522
00:22:49,940 --> 00:22:50,920
Why didn't you tell me

523
00:22:51,280 --> 00:22:52,120
about this?

524
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:54,480
I suspected those three before,

525
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:56,520
but now the leads point to Zhou Qin.

526
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:58,400
The three of them
are no longer relevant.

527
00:22:59,600 --> 00:23:00,480
The thing is,

528
00:23:01,080 --> 00:23:02,520
I don't quite understand something.

529
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:05,320
Don't you think something's odd

530
00:23:05,320 --> 00:23:06,360
about Ouyang Mingyue?

531
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:11,360
Ouyang Mingyue?

532
00:23:12,600 --> 00:23:13,880
But the evidence is solid.

533
00:23:14,600 --> 00:23:15,880
There shouldn't be any issues.

534
00:23:18,600 --> 00:23:19,720
That's right, Xuanxuan.

535
00:23:20,040 --> 00:23:21,320
I think you've been overworking

536
00:23:21,320 --> 00:23:22,320
yourself lately.

537
00:23:22,480 --> 00:23:23,480
Don't overthink it.

538
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:26,200
Your food is here.

539
00:23:27,680 --> 00:23:28,200
Here.

