00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:32,400
To another case solved!

541
00:23:33,360 --> 00:23:35,080
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

542
00:23:37,400 --> 00:23:38,720
This way, please.

543
00:23:42,040 --> 00:23:42,600
This way.

544
00:23:43,320 --> 00:23:44,440
Xuanxuan.

545
00:23:44,760 --> 00:23:46,320
Why won't you drink with me?

546
00:23:47,760 --> 00:23:48,640
