563
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:28,480
Something doesn't add up.

564
00:24:29,280 --> 00:24:30,800
She couldn't have seen it herself.

565
00:24:36,040 --> 00:24:37,240
I know what's wrong!

566
00:24:39,840 --> 00:24:40,480
Zijie.

567
00:24:40,760 --> 00:24:41,680
Let's go home.

568
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:42,680
I've figured it out.

569
00:24:42,680 --> 00:24:43,480
Sun Weiyan.

