00:24:43,480 --> 00:24:44,320
Get back to work.

571
00:24:44,540 --> 00:24:45,480
Have a drink with me

572
00:24:45,480 --> 00:24:46,420
and then we'll leave.

573
00:24:46,440 --> 00:24:47,120
No more drinks.

574
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:47,800
Let's go.

575
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:49,160
Just one more...

576
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:52,920
Get up!

577
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:54,100
- Get up.
- Let's drink...

578
00:24:54,140 --> 00:24:54,540
Come on!

579
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:55,920
I haven't had enough yet...

580
00:24:55,920 --> 00:24:56,400
Let's go.

581
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:57,200
Where are we going?

582
00:24:57,360 --> 00:24:59,360
- Home to drink.
- Home to drink.

583
00:24:59,669 --> 00:25:02,900
(Zhai Residence)

584
00:25:10,400 --> 00:25:11,520
The case is already solved.

585
00:25:11,960 --> 00:25:13,160
What do you want with me now?

586
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:14,480
Calm down, Official Zhou.

587
00:25:15,160 --> 00:25:15,760
Have a seat.

588
00:25:19,080 --> 00:25:20,720
So much has happened in our residence.

589
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:22,800
We can't take

590
00:25:22,800 --> 00:25:24,040
much more.

591
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:26,320
Be patient, everyone.

592
00:25:26,740 --> 00:25:27,680
We've all overlooked

593
00:25:27,680 --> 00:25:29,240
something important.

594
00:25:30,480 --> 00:25:31,120
Bring her in.

595
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:35,360
Young Lady Mingyue.

596
00:25:38,160 --> 00:25:39,640
I've told you everything.

597
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:41,000
What more do you want?

598
00:25:47,720 --> 00:25:48,600
But what you've said

599
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:49,880
isn't the truth.

600
00:25:50,400 --> 00:25:52,480
I saw him kill my father
with my own eyes.

601
00:25:52,720 --> 00:25:54,240
What other truth do you want?

602
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:56,000
Are you sure you saw it
with your own eyes?

603
00:25:56,020 --> 00:25:56,460
Yes.

604
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:58,590
But you were only four or five years old
at the time.

605
00:25:58,600 --> 00:25:59,560
So what?

606
00:26:00,120 --> 00:26:01,240
I'll never forget the hatred

607
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:03,240
of watching my parents killed.

608
00:26:04,120 --> 00:26:04,840
Is it good?

609
00:26:05,760 --> 00:26:06,800
I'll go make you some food.

610
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:12,120
Yue'er.

611
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:13,280
Father!

612
00:26:14,280 --> 00:26:15,200
Yue'er.

613
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:16,360
I've missed you so much.

614
00:26:16,360 --> 00:26:17,160
Did you miss me?

615
00:26:18,300 --> 00:26:19,480
My little girl smells lovely.

616
00:26:21,360 --> 00:26:23,340
Where did you get the money
to buy so much rice?

617
00:26:23,340 --> 00:26:24,380
Your brother gave it to me.

618
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:25,940
He hired me to refine elixirs for him

619
00:26:25,940 --> 00:26:27,020
and paid me for the work.

620
00:26:27,060 --> 00:26:28,360
Don't get too close to him.

621
00:26:28,360 --> 00:26:29,680
My brother...

622
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:31,040
We're family.

623
00:26:31,040 --> 00:26:32,800
It's just keeping things
within the family.

624
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:33,760
Besides,

625
00:26:33,920 --> 00:26:35,120
with this job,

626
00:26:35,280 --> 00:26:36,120
my family

627
00:26:36,120 --> 00:26:37,600
won't have to go hungry anymore.

628
00:26:38,600 --> 00:26:39,120
All right.

629
00:26:39,120 --> 00:26:40,640
Just make sure to take care of yourself

630
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:42,560
and come back early every day.

631
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:43,440
Sure.

632
00:26:43,960 --> 00:26:44,440
Go on,

633
00:26:44,440 --> 00:26:45,260
get some rest inside.

634
00:26:45,260 --> 00:26:46,360
Okay. Let's go home!

635
00:26:46,360 --> 00:26:47,320
Let's head inside!

636
00:26:48,180 --> 00:26:49,500
My daughter smells so nice!

637
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:54,680
The elixir is ready, right?

638
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:56,120
Hand it over!

639
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:12,640
How do you feel?

640
00:27:13,880 --> 00:27:15,840
I don't feel anything at all.

641
00:27:16,560 --> 00:27:17,520
Could there be a problem

642
00:27:17,520 --> 00:27:19,040
with the inducer?

643
00:27:20,040 --> 00:27:21,800
That can't be right.

644
00:27:32,320 --> 00:27:32,880
Look here.

645
00:27:33,560 --> 00:27:34,480
It says

646
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:38,240
to achieve the best longevity effects,

647
00:27:38,880 --> 00:27:40,240
the inducer must be

648
00:27:40,240 --> 00:27:41,840
someone born

649
00:27:41,840 --> 00:27:43,440
in a year, month,

650
00:27:43,600 --> 00:27:44,920
and day of Yang.

651
00:27:45,640 --> 00:27:46,200
Where am I

652
00:27:46,440 --> 00:27:48,440
supposed to find such a person?

653
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:53,680
Someone born
in a year, month, and day of Yang.

654
00:27:54,720 --> 00:27:55,640
I just remembered.

655
00:27:56,120 --> 00:27:58,120
My brother-in-law fits the criteria.

656
00:27:59,080 --> 00:28:01,080
But he's your brother-in-law.

657
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:02,160
And using a person

658
00:28:02,400 --> 00:28:04,120
as a medicine inducer

659
00:28:04,520 --> 00:28:06,520
would kill them.

660
00:28:06,800 --> 00:28:08,080
Can your sister

661
00:28:08,280 --> 00:28:09,600
accept that?

662
00:28:10,200 --> 00:28:11,160
I don't care,

663
00:28:11,320 --> 00:28:12,440
not if it's for the elixir.

664
00:28:14,840 --> 00:28:15,880
This is what we'll do.

665
00:28:26,760 --> 00:28:27,960
Today's batch turned out great.

666
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:28,400
You should

667
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:29,160
try it later.

668
00:28:29,360 --> 00:28:30,360
All right.

669
00:28:31,280 --> 00:28:32,360
Here's double your pay

670
00:28:32,760 --> 00:28:33,520
for today.

671
00:28:34,280 --> 00:28:35,360
We're family.

672
00:28:35,360 --> 00:28:36,780
You don't need to be so generous.

673
00:28:36,800 --> 00:28:38,440
You've already treated my sister

674
00:28:38,440 --> 00:28:39,360
well enough.

675
00:28:39,360 --> 00:28:41,360
She's never had to suffer.

676
00:28:41,360 --> 00:28:42,560
Not at all.

677
00:28:47,700 --> 00:28:48,900
What are you waiting for?

678
00:28:48,920 --> 00:28:49,980
Hurry and help!

679
00:28:50,360 --> 00:28:51,000
Quickly!

680
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:04,680
That's how it all happened back then.

681
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:05,520
All right.

682
00:29:06,080 --> 00:29:07,160
As you said,

683
00:29:07,840 --> 00:29:09,200
there were only three people

684
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:10,440
in the alchemy room.

685
00:29:10,500 --> 00:29:11,760
Master Zhai, the Longhu Priest,

686
00:29:11,760 --> 00:29:12,960
and your father.

687
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:14,320
Where were you?

688
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:19,560
I was hiding outside the window.

689
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:21,880
Those two scoundrels didn't see me.

690
00:29:22,600 --> 00:29:23,840
That's how I managed

691
00:29:24,600 --> 00:29:25,960
to escape.

692
00:29:38,760 --> 00:29:40,280
If you remember everything so clearly,

693
00:29:40,920 --> 00:29:41,920
do you recall

694
00:29:42,320 --> 00:29:43,160
the alchemy furnace?

695
00:29:43,600 --> 00:29:44,240
Of course.

696
00:29:44,720 --> 00:29:46,400
The furnace had my father's blood on it.

697
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:47,880
I'll never forget that.

698
00:29:48,360 --> 00:29:49,400
Can you draw it?

699
00:29:49,640 --> 00:29:50,480
Of course.

700
00:29:51,760 --> 00:29:52,880
Bring the ink and paper.

701
00:29:53,140 --> 00:29:56,220
(Zhai Residence)

702
00:30:05,880 --> 00:30:07,080
Is this the furnace?

703
00:30:07,560 --> 00:30:08,360
The exact one?

704
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:09,920
The exact one.

705
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:14,280
Everyone, take a look.

706
00:30:16,520 --> 00:30:17,360
This furnace

707
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:19,360
looks familiar.

708
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:20,320
I think so too.

709
00:30:20,400 --> 00:30:22,240
I feel like I've seen it
somewhere before.

710
00:30:23,560 --> 00:30:24,680
I recognize this furnace.

711
00:30:24,980 --> 00:30:26,500
It's the royal alchemy furnace.

712
00:30:26,800 --> 00:30:27,640
Three years ago,

713
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:29,640
before His Majesty
ascended to the throne,

714
00:30:29,760 --> 00:30:31,860
the late emperor,
obsessed with Taoism and alchemy,

715
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:33,040
gifted this furnace

716
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:34,560
to Master Ge.

717
00:30:35,320 --> 00:30:36,640
Master Ge's temple

718
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:39,320
is located over 50 kilometers
from Yan City in Liang City.

719
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:40,880
The late emperor

720
00:30:41,200 --> 00:30:42,400
sent a heavily armed escort

721
00:30:43,600 --> 00:30:45,080
to transport it from the capital.

722
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:46,660
That's right.

723
00:30:46,720 --> 00:30:47,640
Now I remember.

724
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:49,760
When the furnace
passed through Yan City,

725
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:51,360
Mingyue and I went to see it.

726
00:30:51,840 --> 00:30:52,480
That's right.

727
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:54,640
Master took the two young ladies there

728
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:55,520
to gain experience.

729
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:57,680
I also went along.

730
00:31:01,720 --> 00:31:03,800
Make way!

731
00:31:06,520 --> 00:31:07,760
Mingyue, look!

732
00:31:07,760 --> 00:31:09,360
That furnace is magnificent.

733
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:10,100
Of course, it is.

734
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:12,320
That's the furnace
His Majesty gifted to Master Ge.

735
00:31:12,320 --> 00:31:13,640
How could it be ordinary?

736
00:31:14,520 --> 00:31:15,880
It's just a furnace.

737
00:31:16,080 --> 00:31:17,680
What's so special about it?

738
00:31:25,760 --> 00:31:26,800
You just said

739
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:29,120
you saw this furnace
with your own eyes.

740
00:31:29,560 --> 00:31:30,640
But this furnace

741
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:31,720
only arrived in Yanzhou

742
00:31:31,720 --> 00:31:32,760
three years ago.

743
00:31:33,080 --> 00:31:34,160
How could you have seen it?

744
00:31:36,440 --> 00:31:37,520
Right...

745
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:41,440
I heard that when alchemy

746
00:31:42,440 --> 00:31:43,960
was prevalent over ten years ago,

747
00:31:44,640 --> 00:31:46,640
saltpeter was used in the processes.

748
00:31:47,440 --> 00:31:49,240
However,
the smell of saltpeter is pungent

749
00:31:49,760 --> 00:31:51,200
and can cause dizziness and vomiting

750
00:31:51,200 --> 00:31:52,280
when inhaled too much.

751
00:31:52,280 --> 00:31:53,880
Even alchemists themselves

752
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:55,840
had to cover their faces
with wet cloths.

753
00:31:55,960 --> 00:31:58,100
You were only four or five years old
at the time.

754
00:31:58,120 --> 00:31:59,400
Why would your father take you

755
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:00,480
to such a place?

756
00:32:01,280 --> 00:32:02,400
And in your memory,

757
00:32:02,400 --> 00:32:04,720
you said you could clearly see
all their faces.

758
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:07,000
None of their faces

759
00:32:07,280 --> 00:32:08,080
were covered.

760
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:15,160
Master was obsessed with alchemy,

761
00:32:15,400 --> 00:32:16,480
and I know

762
00:32:16,600 --> 00:32:17,680
a little about it.

763
00:32:18,040 --> 00:32:19,680
Alchemy requires saltpeter

764
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:21,040
and demands extreme caution.

765
00:32:21,620 --> 00:32:23,740
Not only must the nose and mouth
be protected,

766
00:32:23,760 --> 00:32:24,820
but even the eyes

767
00:32:24,860 --> 00:32:26,340
must be covered with gauze.

768
00:32:26,480 --> 00:32:27,600
There have been many cases

769
00:32:27,660 --> 00:32:29,460
of people being poisoned
by saltpeter fumes.

770
00:32:29,540 --> 00:32:30,460
Master was always

771
00:32:30,520 --> 00:32:31,520
very careful.

772
00:32:31,760 --> 00:32:32,840
It's impossible for him

773
00:32:32,880 --> 00:32:35,200
not to have taken
any protective measures.

774
00:32:35,720 --> 00:32:37,120
But I saw them!

775
00:32:38,120 --> 00:32:39,800
Human memory is fragmented.

776
00:32:40,160 --> 00:32:41,520
If it's not coherent,

777
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:43,240
your mind fills in the gaps

778
00:32:43,240 --> 00:32:44,940
based on your thoughts and concepts.

779
00:32:45,160 --> 00:32:46,360
And if someone constantly

780
00:32:46,520 --> 00:32:48,520
suggests ideas to you
during this process,

781
00:32:48,880 --> 00:32:49,640
your brain

782
00:32:50,040 --> 00:32:51,560
can create a false

783
00:32:51,920 --> 00:32:53,040
yet seemingly real memory.

784
00:32:53,800 --> 00:32:54,640
This technique

785
00:32:55,040 --> 00:32:55,680
is called

786
00:32:55,840 --> 00:32:57,200
memory implantation.

787
00:33:27,961 --> 00:33:33,841
♪Like the setting sun,
which repeatedly sets in the west♪

788
00:33:35,101 --> 00:33:40,541
♪My heart goes over mountains
to rest with you♪

789
00:33:41,701 --> 00:33:45,141
♪As the winds and clouds shift,
our encounter♪

790
00:33:45,141 --> 00:33:48,901
♪Seems like the perfect foreshadowing♪

791
00:33:49,301 --> 00:33:54,341
♪But it was a misplaced expectation♪

792
00:33:55,861 --> 00:33:58,941
♪I think I'm exceptionally affectionate♪

793
00:33:59,141 --> 00:34:02,061
♪Devotion can warm the coldest ice♪

794
00:34:02,421 --> 00:34:05,621
♪And you're a shooting star
that flashes by♪

795
00:34:06,061 --> 00:34:08,341
♪Out of reach♪

796
00:34:09,421 --> 00:34:12,621
♪I prayed for a miracle countless times♪

797
00:34:12,901 --> 00:34:17,021
♪If I meet you, I only wish
we could be together forever♪

798
00:34:17,301 --> 00:34:23,421
♪But only the distant phantom remains♪

799
00:34:23,541 --> 00:34:26,581
♪Love rises like the wind
but remains unsettled when it stops♪

800
00:34:26,861 --> 00:34:29,861
♪Chasing you through four seasons,
wandering for a lifetime♪

801
00:34:30,141 --> 00:34:31,821
♪Fish in the water♪

802
00:34:31,821 --> 00:34:37,061
♪Is greedy for the reflection
of clouds in the heart of the lake♪

803
00:34:37,261 --> 00:34:40,181
♪From dusk to dawn,
from heavy snow to early clear sky♪

804
00:34:40,381 --> 00:34:44,701
♪Searching for your footprints
from south to west♪

805
00:34:45,061 --> 00:34:50,701
♪The wind stops,
but the dream isn't over♪
